
List of variables used:
features- dataframe, with list of feature variable
activity_labels- data frame with activity labels
y_test- data frame with the activities as numbers
x_test- data frame with the quantities assigned to features
subject_test- data frame with the subjects 
test_data- data frame with all the test data 
y_train- data frame with the activities as numbers
x_train- data frame with the quantities assigned to features
subject_train- data frame with the subjects 
train_data- data frame with all the train data 
total_data- data frame with the training and testing data merged
mean_std_data- data frame with only mean and standard deviation feature variables
merged_data- Same data frame as the mean_std_data, with the features and activities labeled more appropriately
final_data- data frame summarized by mean of each subject and activity
